hould I?"],[3903,4104,"Nah, let's go together."],[4154,4375,"No, Mrs. Langford and Teddy"],[4375,4517,"will come for you, I swear."],[4592,4713,"Mrs. Langford?"],[4821,4938,"Oh yeah."],[5067,5255,"You're not really Teddy's sister."],[5397,5613,"You're just the maid's daughter."],[5613,5684,"What?"],[5709,5834,"The maid's daughter?"],[5847,6043,"That's even lower than where I stand."],[6118,6452,"Yeah, I might just be the maid's daughter,"],[6452,6673,"but I'm not even from your guys' world,"],[6673,6865,"so can you please just let me go?"],[6956,7065,"Let you go?"],[7090,7152,"Come on."],[7198,7349,"A maid's daughter probably knows"],[7349,7494,"how to please real well."],[7520,7732,"I heard you've got Teddy hooked."],[7778,7953,"I'd like to see what that's like."],[7978,8041,"Yeah."],[8087,8237,"Can't get the rich kid's sister?"],[8274,8354,"Whatever."],[8404,8533,"We'll settle for the maid."],[8583,8771,"Just for one night, I'll play the prince."],[8854,8921,"No!"]],"49":[[0,79,"Don't touch me!"],[91,137,"No!"],[137,250,"Get away from me!"],[450,546,"You bitch!"],[579,742,"You think you can threaten me?"],[771,900,"You're just a maid."],[921,1076,"Even after I wreck you,"],[1113,1238,"they'll just throw some hush money"],[1238,1347,"around at best."],[1376,1514,"They'll throw you aside,"],[1514,1676,"so you don't say a word."],[1697,1864,"He will come for me."],[1864,2014,"He's not gonna leave me here."],[2014,2127,"He won't abandon me."],[2127,2227,"I know he won't."],[2285,2448,"Oh, you're so naive."],[2477,2669,"You think your precious savior,"],[2669,2952,"Teddy, is gonna come rescue you?"],[3044,3211,"I could kill you right now."],[3274,3470,"Nobody would ever care."],[3486,3703,"Nobody would ever notice."],[3791,4016,"So just because I'm a maid"],[4016,4237,"means that I don't deserve to live?"],[4250,4471,"And that I should just give up fighting?"],[4546,4662,"You're insane!"],[5067,5167,"You bitch!"],[5271,5434,"Still trying to play games?"],[5555,5864,"Pl